OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FPeople in Carlisle, Workington, and
OL,7,Frural Whitehaven reported the highest
OL,8,Frates of suicidal thoughts in Cumbria,
OL,9,Faccording to a report into suicide
OL,10,Fcommissioned by Cumberland Council.
OL,12,F'The Big Question' analysed 782
OL,13,Fresponses to explore experiences
OL,14,Frelated to suicide in Cumberland.
OL,16,FAccording to the council, its local
OL,17,Fauthority area has the third highest
OL,18,Frate of suicide in England, at 19.4
OL,19,Fsuicides per 100,000 people - compared
OL,20,Fto the England-wide average of 10.9
OL,21,Fper 100,000.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
