PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FThe report, conducted in partnership
OL,7,Fwith Liverpool John Moores University,
OL,8,Falso found that women reported
OL,9,F"slightly higher" levels of having
OL,10,Fexperienced suicidal thoughts, and
OL,11,Fwere most likely to have attempted
OL,12,Fsuicide.
OL,14,FLisa Birdsall, a suicide campaigner
OL,15,Fwho lost her brother to suicide, told
OL,16,FITV Border: "This research project has
OL,17,Fbrought out some really quite vital
OL,18,Finformation that we can now use to
OL,19,Fhelp shape our support services in
OL,20,Fthis county."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
