PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FAll respondents who identified as
OL,7,F'other', rather than man or woman,
OL,8,Fsaid they had experienced suicidal
OL,9,Fthoughts. The report said this
OL,10,F"(highlighted) the need for inclusive
OL,11,Fand identity-affirming support."
OL,13,FIn total over half of respondents to
OL,14,Fthe survey had previously experienced
OL,15,Fsuicidal or self-harm thoughts. 28% of
OL,16,Fthose surveyed had self-harmed, while
OL,17,F19% had attempted suicide.
OL,26,@rD@BpmrD@Npn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
