PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FNot all of the participants who
OL,7,Freported these thoughts had sought
OL,8,Fhelp or support, with adults aged 60-
OL,9,F79 the least likely to receive support
OL,10,Fafter self-harming.
OL,12,FResidents of Whitehaven and
OL,13,FCockermouth were cited as being some
OL,14,Fof the least likely to receive support
OL,15,Ffollowing self-harm thoughts.
OL,17,FThe report said that this "highlights
OL,18,Fa major opportunity for early
OL,19,Fintervention".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
