FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FIn Whitehaven, a new walk-in mental
OL,7,Fhealth facility has opened which could
OL,8,Fplay a role in tackling the area's
OL,9,Fmental health challenges.
OL,11,F57 people also took part in in-depth
OL,12,Finterviews and focus groups for the
OL,13,Freport, and physical and social
OL,14,Fisolation were "described as a
OL,15,Fdefining feature of life in
OL,16,FCumberland".
OL,18,FPublic transport was seen as a "major
OL,19,Fbarrier" to receiving support, while
OL,20,Fsome participants pointed to
OL,21,Ffragmented rural communities.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
