PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FOne participant said: "You used to
OL,7,Fwander through the village, and
OL,8,Feverybody knew you... now there's just
OL,9,Fa lack of belonging."
OL,11,F'The Big Question' report's first
OL,12,Fsuggestion on tackling poor mental
OL,13,Fhealth in Cumberland is to strengthen
OL,14,Faccess to support and early
OL,15,Fintervention.
OL,17,FIt suggested targeting women with
OL,18,Fsuicide support, and encouraged the
OL,19,Fuse of "discreet community hubs" and
OL,20,Fmobile "Wheels of Wellness" services
OL,21,Ffor rural areas.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FTo reduce suicide support disparities
OL,7,Fbetween areas, the report suggested
OL,8,Fconducting 90-day audits town-by-town
OL,9,Fto map access to mental health support.
OL,11,FIt concluded that "suicide prevention
OL,12,Fin Cumberland must prioritise early,
OL,13,Fequitable, and compassionate
OL,14,Fintervention."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
