PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FCllr Justin McDermott, Cumberland
OL,7,FCouncil Portfolio Holder for Public
OL,8,FHealth and Communities, said: "This
OL,9,Freport carries a powerful message of
OL,10,Fhope, and I want to say thank you to
OL,11,Feveryone who participated - your
OL,12,Fcourage will drive forward the change
OL,13,Fwe so desperately need.
OL,15,F"This is only the beginning and to
OL,16,Fchange the narrative, we must embed
OL,17,Fthe vision of Zero Suicide Cumberland
OL,18,Fin all of our communities, in
OL,19,Feverything we do."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
