PN,35409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774526572
OL,3,CThe Cumbrian areas where people are
OL,4,Cmost likely to have suicidal thoughts
OL,6,FColin Cox, Director of Public Health,
OL,7,FCustomer and Community Wellbeing said:
OL,8,F"This report shines a light on an
OL,9,Fissue that affects all our communities.
OL,11,F"Understanding the experiences of
OL,12,Fthose in crisis helps us act early to
OL,13,Fsave lives.
OL,15,F"Suicide prevention is everyone's
OL,16,Fresponsibility, and these findings
OL,17,Fwill guide how we deliver services
OL,18,Facross Cumberland to reach people
OL,19,Fbefore they reach crisis."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
